    (LP: #1390152)

 -- Jason Gerard DeRose <jason@system76.com>  Fri, 16 Jan 2015 13:13:55 -0700

system76-driver (14.10.5) utopic; urgency=low

  * Also add `internal_mic_gain` action back for daru4, gazp9b, and kudp1b,
    likewise still needed on Utopic
  * system76driver/daemon.py: add a number of small optimizations that in total
    mean that support for the airplane mode hotkey (Haswell gen laptops) incurs
    around half the events per second and less than a quarter of the CPU usage
    (as measured by `powertop`)
  * Drop `wifi_pm_disable` action from all Haswell gen laptops as the latest
    3.16 kernel plus the latest linux-firmware package seem to have completely
    fixed the latency, reliability, and performance issues previously
    encountered when power management was turned on for Intel 3160/7260 cards

 -- Jason Gerard DeRose <jason@system76.com>  Wed, 10 Dec 2014 16:49:57 -0700

