system76-driver (14.10.0) utopic; urgency=low

  * Start 14.10.x series, initial Utopic release
  * Drop `disable_power_well` action as it's no longer needed for Haswell
    laptop products with the Linux 3.16 kernel (LP: #1356507)
  * Switch from `acpi_video0` to `intel_backlight` on all Haswell products,
    use 75% of max_brightness for default brightness (LP: #1375477)
  * debian/system76-driver.upstart: in order to fix backlight brightness
    restore, "start on (login-session-start or desktop-session-start)"
    (LP: #1378974)
  * Drop `internal_mic_gain` action from daru4, galu1, gazp9b, and kudp1b, as
    its no longer needed on Utopic
  * debian/control: `system76-driver-nvidia` now Depends on
    (nvidia-343 | nvidia-331-updates)
  * system76-nvidia-quirks: change Handler to "nvidia-343|nvidia-331-updates"

